// Changeling = a CDA ([CR#702.73a,604.3]): "this object is every creature
// type", functioning everywhere — the open-set subtype fill
// (Modification::AllCreatureTypes, [CR#205.3m]'s open list) on a
// CDA-flagged static. The layer engine's fill is the kw-changeling seam.
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Changeling",
    template: "changeling",
    abilities: [Static(
        cda: true,
        effects: [Modify(of: Of(This), changes: [AllCreatureTypes])],
    )],
)
